ds/release/6861662|title=Laura Marano \u2013 Words|work=Discogs|accessdate=March 29, 2015}}</ref>\n| 2010\n| {{n/a|Non-album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I Love Christmas\"<ref name=ILoveChristmas/><br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Ross Lynch]])</span>\n| 2013\n| ''[[Holidays Unwrapped]]''\n|}\n\n===Other appearances===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Other artist(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Shine\"\n| 2012\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n| ''[[Disney Fairies: Faith, Trust and Pixie Dust]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"The Me That You Don't See\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2014\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Disney Channel: Play It Loud]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"''Austin & Ally'' Glee Club Mash Up\"\n| Ross Lynch, [[Calum Worthy]] and [[Raini Rodriguez]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"You Can Come to Me\"\n| Ross Lynch\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Title\n! Year\n! Director(s)\n! Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Words\"\n| 2010\n| Waldman Entertainment\n| <ref>{{cite web|author= |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gc_WwEFLuUY|title=Laura Marano- Words (Official Music Video)|via=YouTube |date= |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"The Me That You Don't See\"\n| 2013\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{unknown}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|author= |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BHPB2cR2IaQ |title=Laura Marano - The Me That You Don't See (Official Video) |via=YouTube |date= |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"For The Ride\"\n| 2015\n| <ref>{{cite web|author= |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6X79ZfOWUrg |title=Laura Marano - For The Ride (From \"Bad Hair Day\") |via=YouTube |date= |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Boombox (song)|Boombox]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2016\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Cole Walliser]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|auth