 2012|accessdate=July 13, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Somebody to You]]\"\n| 2014\n| [[The Vamps (British band)|The Vamps]] and [[Demi Lovato]]\n| Emil Nava\n| <ref>{{cite web|author= |url=//www.youtube.com/watch?v=0go2nfVXFgA |title=The Vamps - Somebody To You ft. Demi Lovato |via=YouTube |date= |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Freya Vs. Ravenna\"\n| 2016\n| [[Princess Rap Battle]]\n| [[Whitney Avalon]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=55Ej8AoKCRQ |title=Freya Vs. Ravenna Princess Rap Battle |via=YouTube |date= |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|Year  \n!scope=\"col\"|Award\n!scope=\"col\"|Category\n!scope=\"col\"|Work\n!scope=\"col\"|Result \n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"|{{Abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n|2014\n|[[Teen Choice Awards]]\n|Choice TV Actress: Comedy\n|''[[Austin & Ally]]''\n|{{Nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite news|author=Philiana Ng|title=Teen Choice Awards Nominees: Selena Gomez, Austin Mahone and More|url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2014/06/17/teen-choice-awards-nominations-2014-nominees-full-list|accessdate=June 17, 2014|date=June 17, 2014|work=Hollywood Life}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|2015\n|[[Kids' Choice Awards]]\n|Favorite TV Actress\n|''Austin & Ally''\n|{{Won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite news|author=Rebecca Macatee|title=2015 Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Awards Honor Nick Jones,Meryl Streep: See the Complete List of Nominees!|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/627610/2015-nickelodeon-s-kids-choice-awards-honor-nick-jonas-meryl-streep-see-the-complete-list-of-nominees |work=E! Online  |date=February 20, 2015 |accessdate=August 6, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|Remi Awards\n|Rising Actress\n|''[[A Sort of Homecoming (film)|A Sort of Homecoming]]''\n|{{Won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"robly.com\" />\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Teen Choice Awards]]\n|Choice Summer TV Star: Female\n|''Austin & Ally''